OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1783682373
OL,3,CMan arrested on suspicion of murder
OL,4,Cafter fatal crash
OL,6,FA collision between two cars which
OL,7,Fresulted in the death of an elderly
OL,8,Fwoman is now being treated as murder,
OL,9,Fpolice said.
OL,11,FThe crash happened on the B4696, near
OL,12,FRoyal Wootton Bassett in Wiltshire, on
OL,13,Fthe evening of June 30.
OL,15,FWiltshire Police said the collision
OL,16,Finvolved an orange Peugeot 107
OL,17,Ftravelling northbound and a black
OL,18,FVauxhall Astra travelling southbound.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
