OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1783682373
OL,3,CMan arrested on suspicion of murder
OL,4,Cafter fatal crash
OL,6,FThe driver of the Peugeot, a woman in
OL,7,Fher 70s, was declared dead at the
OL,8,Fscene.
OL,10,FA passenger in the Vauxhall, a teenage
OL,11,Fgirl, suffered serious injuries in the
OL,12,Fcollision and was taken to hospital,
OL,13,Fwhere she remains.
OL,15,FPolice said the driver of the
OL,16,FVauxhall, a man aged 43, has been
OL,17,Ffurther arrested on suspicion of
OL,18,Fmurder and attempted murder.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1783682373
OL,3,CMan arrested on suspicion of murder
OL,4,Cafter fatal crash
OL,6,FHe was taken to hospital for treatment
OL,7,Ffollowing the collision and has now
OL,8,Fbeen taken into custody for
OL,9,Fquestioning.
OL,11,FThe Wiltshire force has made a
OL,12,Fmandatory referral to the Independent
OL,13,FOffice for Police Conduct (IOPC) due
OL,14,Fto previous involvement with the
OL,15,Fsuspect.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
