OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1783682373
OL,3,CMan arrested on suspicion of murder
OL,4,Cafter fatal crash
OL,6,FDetective Chief Inspector Phil Walker,
OL,7,Fwho is leading the investigation,
OL,8,Fsaid: "Following initial enquiries, I
OL,9,Fcan confirm this collision is now
OL,10,Fbeing treated as a murder
OL,11,Finvestigation and the suspect has been
OL,12,Fre-arrested on suspicion of murder.
OL,14,F"My thoughts continue to be with the
OL,15,Fvictim's family and all that knew her.
OL,16,FHer next of kin have been informed of
OL,17,Fthis latest development in the
OL,18,Finvestigation and they continue to be
OL,19,Fsupported by specially trained
OL,20,Fofficers.
OL,26,@pD@GOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1783682373
OL,3,CMan arrested on suspicion of murder
OL,4,Cafter fatal crash
OL,6,F"I appreciate this update may increase
OL,7,Fcommunity concern, however please be
OL,8,Freassured that there is no risk to the
OL,9,Fwider public and we are working to
OL,10,Fpiece together the events which led to
OL,11,Fthis tragic incident.
OL,13,F"We remain keen to hear from any
OL,14,Fwitnesses or anyone who might have
OL,15,Fdash cam footage from the area of the
OL,16,Fcollision at the time.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
