CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1783682373
OL,3,CMan arrested on suspicion of murder
OL,4,Cafter fatal crash
OL,6,F"In addition, any witnesses who have
OL,7,Fdash cam footage of a black Vauxhall
OL,8,FAstra from Cricklade High Street,
OL,9,FPurton High Street, and surrounding
OL,10,Fareas on Tuesday June 30th."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@\O]
